      "content": "wait really?? that sounds so scary. i just looked up some symptoms online and a lot of people say that sharp pain during deep breaths is just pleurisy or even just acid reflux from the airplane food. i dont really want to go to a hospital in a foreign country if i dont have to, it's gonna be so expensive and stressful. are you sure it's not just something minor like that? i feel like if i just take some antacids and try to relax i'll be fine.",
